"description": "<p>Hi there! We are Sanction Scanner, a B2B SaaS Fintech company that prevents Financial Crime for its clients around the world. We are providing different Intelligent software with AI and Machine Learning technologies.</p><p></p><p>Sanction Scanner is trusted by 300+ brands from high-growth fintech to legacy high street banks and many prestigious companies like Iron Source, Unity, Papara, Koc, DLL, and the list goes on.</p><p></p><p>Our team believes in Innovation and keeps updating themselves always. We work closely with other Departments with agile teams, and we are not afraid of getting our hands dirty.</p><p>We are looking for Performance Marketing Specialist for accessing new Brands and countries, who will help and explain to them how Sanction Scanner prevents new clients from Financial Crime.</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul> <li>Managing ad channels (LinkedIn, Instagram, Facebook, Twitter) Accounts</li> <li>Developing creative ideas with other teams for related channels</li> <li>Ability to manage strategies and processes in studies on new customer acquisition</li> <li>Tracking and reporting of customers' traffic and conversions with web analytics tools</li> </ul><ul> <li>Experienced in the use of reporting and tracking tools such as Google Search Console, Google Analytics, Google Tag Manager, Hubspot, Semrush, Ahrefs, GTMetrix, LightHouse.</li> <li>Experienced in SEO.</li> <li>Experienced in social media (LinkedIn, Instagram, Facebook) management and reporting.</li> <li>Experienced HTML editing is a plus</li> <li>Excellent written and oral communication skills in English.</li> </ul><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><p></p><ul> <li> <strong>A Competitive Compensation Package </strong>-  NET Salary payment with additional fringe benefits.</li> <li> <strong>A meal compensation</strong> that is actually enough for a decent &amp; nutritious lunc</li> <li> <strong>Inclusive Health Benefits</strong> - We are here for you with comprehensive support whenever you need it</li> <li> <strong>Strong Appreciation and Reward Culture</strong> - Your impact on Sanction Scanner’s grow will be appreciated</li> <li> <strong>Digital Membership Support </strong>- A balance you can use for your digital memberships.</li> <li> <strong>Learning never ends! </strong>Training budget to help you grow in your role, gain new skills, and learn new things!</li> <li> <strong>No Dress Code. </strong>Dress as you like.</li> <li> <strong>Dream Team</strong>. Be a part of great team and grow together</li> <li> <strong>Software support.</strong> Subscription to any software you might need to perform at your best</li> <li> <strong>Experience an international work environment</strong> that fosters positive energy through a caring team.</li> <li> <strong>Be a part of shaping the future of Sanction Scanner </strong>by joining our innovative creators.</li> </ul><p> </p><p>We provide equal opportunity to all, we do not discriminate based on gender, sexual orientation, disabilities, religion, or social origin.</p><p></p><ul><li>If you are interested in this job, you can apply via LinkedIn with an updated CV.</li></ul>",
